short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open your CircleCI pipelines directly from a GitHub repository, PR or release tag.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Features
- Open a CircleCI project directly from a GitHub repository
- Open a CircleCI project filtered by PR from a GitHub pull request
- Open a CircleCI project filtered by release tag from a GitHub release
